------------------------------------
Changes in Jnotify (java)
------------------------------------
17.8.2006  : Omry : jnotify-0.9 released
16.8.2006  : Omry : fixed a bug that caused no event to be fired for a file created in an automatic (recursive) watch (Thanks Kristof Nidzwetzki for bug report),
16.8.2006  : Omry : fixed output file name for deleted event (Thanks Kristof Nidzwetzki for bug report).
30/7/2006  : Omry : Added NO_SUCH_FILE_OR_DIRECTORY constant to JNotifyException (Thanks Marcelo Fern√°ndez for feature request).
24/6/2006  : Omry : fixed recursive listening on linux (NPE was thrown in certain cases).
15/12/2005 : Omry : No longer outputs absolute root path in events.
15/12/2005 : Omry : API Cleanup : got rid of the get() method in JNotify. moved constants from IJnotify to JNotify
15/12/2005 : Omry : Fixed bugs with the Linux impl (java side).